[nomarkup][BOOM! Powdered debris fall from the cracks forming in the ceiling as the club is rocked by an explosion.][/nomarkup]
-> {$pcName}: [nomarkup][Explosions? What, do they have bombs?!][/nomarkup]
{$kieran}: We need to go soon; we don’t have long before the entire building comes down.
-> {$pcName}: [nomarkup][Your eyes are still wide in shock, but you do your best to hold it together.][/nomarkup] Right.
[nomarkup][A few patrons who run towards the exits barely make it a few steps before they are filled with lead - mown down in a mist of blood.][/nomarkup]
<<if GetIsPartyMemberRecruited("ANASTASIA") is true>>
    {$anastasia}: [nomarkup][She turns back to look at the two of you.][/nomarkup] Y’know, I really don’t think they’re going to be receptive to cookie sales from you Girl Scouts gossiping back there… What’s the plan?
