    {$anastasia}: Dunno. They’re moving too fast and I can’t — [nomarkup][She responds, but shuts up quickly mid-sentence.][/nomarkup]
<<endif>>
{kieran}: [nomarkup][Kieran cocks his head to the side and closes his eyes, muttering to himself for a few long moments.][/nomarkup] Five at the entrance with guns, and at least one of the patrons has returned fire.
<<if GetIsPartyMemberRecruited("ANASTASIA") is true>>
    {$anastasia}: Automatic, semi? What’s the fire rate?
