    <<if Roll ("Wits","Insight")>=4>>
        [nomarkup][Oddly, despite the fact that both of them were arguing just minutes ago, they seem to be on the same page in this dire circumstance - both using their powers to gather information and possibly gain an edge over the gunmen assaulting the club they’re all trapped inside. This is a synergy that they’d never show unless their next moves could be their last… You just hope you won’t have to try and get them to admit they make a good team, in the aftermath.][/nomarkup]
    <<endif>>
    {$kieran}: Semiautomatic. We’ll have just enough time to make a run for it, once they stop to reload.
<<endif>>
